SliTaz Website
================================================================================


The SliTaz website is hand made, use PHP and XHTML 1.0 Transitional. Code must
follow standards and be validated by the W3C. We have a main index with news,
feed parser, Tweets and link to all website languages. Since we Tweet and blog
only in English, we diplay these news only on the main page but website news
are translated.


================================================================================
